  <main class="page">
    <header class="hero">
      <div class="hero__lede">
        <h1 class="hero__name">Ron Bronson</h1>
        <p class="hero__tagline">Multilateral public delivery</p>
      </div>
      <figure class="hero__portrait">
        <img src="/ron-bronson.jpg" alt="Ron Bronson" />
      </figure>
    </header>
    <section class="section">
      <p class="lede">
       The gap between what government decides and what actually reaches people is the most important design problem there is. I've spent twenty years designing services, leading teams, advising leaders, and improving the public tech stack from the ground up for millions of people.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section class="section">
      <h2>Currently</h2>
      <p>
       Currently: Occupant/State Capacity AI, Assistant Professor of Practice in Urban Technology at the University of Michigan Taubman College of Architecture and Urban Planning. 
Past: 18F, Nava, PDX Digital Corps
      </p>
